Package health.viewers

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Observer
    This class is the interface used by the Viewers which implements the observer pattern.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BarGraph
    This class represents a Viewer of type BarGraph, which is attached to the Model and creates a Bar Graph according to the data in the Model.
    LineGraph
    This class represents a Viewer of type LineGraph, which is attached to the Model and creates a Line Graph according to the data in the Model.
    PieGraph
    This class represents a Viewer of type PieGraph, which is attached to the Model and creates a Pie Graph according to the data in the Model.
    Report
    This class represents a Viewer of type Report, which is attached to the Model and creates a Text representation of the Model.
    ScatterGraph
    This class represents a Viewer of type ScatterGraph, which is attached to the Model and creates a Scatter Graph according to the data in the Model.
    Subject
    Subject is the superclass of the Model which holds the list of Observers(implemented as Viewers).
    Viewer
    Viewer is the superclass from which all the different types of viewers inherit from.
